OL,3,CSuspect charged with arson after
OL,4,Creports of fire at former synagogue
OL,6,FA 45-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith arson with intent to endanger
OL,8,Flife after reports of a fire at a
OL,9,Fformer synagogue in east London.
OL,11,FMoses Edwards, from Wanstead, will
OL,12,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt on Tuesday after the alleged
OL,14,Farson attack on the building in Nelson
OL,15,FStreet, Whitechapel on May 5.
OL,17,FPolice said minor damage was caused to
OL,18,Fthe gates and a lock at the front of
OL,19,Fthe building shortly after 5am, and no
OL,20,Fone was hurt.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
