OL,3,CSuspect charged with arson after
OL,4,Creports of fire at former synagogue
OL,6,FThe building is in the process of
OL,7,Fbeing sold to a Muslim organisation
OL,8,Fwhich plans to turn it into a mosque
OL,9,Fand community centre.
OL,11,FThe incident was one of a series of
OL,12,Fseparate alleged arson attacks that
OL,13,Fhave targeted Jewish sites in London
OL,14,Fin the past two months.
OL,16,FA 52-year-old woman, who was also
OL,17,Farrested as part of the investigation,
OL,18,Fhas been released on bail to a date in
OL,19,FAugust.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
